@[simp]
theorem trace_zero : trace (0 : matrix n n R) = 0 :=
  (finset.sum_const (0 : R)).trans <| smul_zero _
#align trace_zero trace_zero

trace_sub:

theorem trace_sub (A B : matrix n n R) : trace (A - B) = trace A - trace B :=
  finset.sum_sub_distrib

trace_smul:

trace_one:
@[simp]
theorem trace_one : trace (1 : matrix n n R) = fintype.card n := by
  simp_rw [trace, diag_one, pi.one_def, finset.sum_const, nsmul_one, finset.card_univ]
#align trace_one trace_one
trace_neg:
@[simp]
theorem trace_neg (A : matrix n n R) : trace (-A) = -trace A :=
  finset.sum_neg_distrib
#align trace_neg trace_neg
trace_multiset_sum:
@[simp]
theorem trace_multiset_sum (s : Multiset (matrix n n R)) : trace s.sum = (s.map trace).sum :=
  map_multiset_sum (trace_add_monoid_hom n R) s
#align trace_multiset_sum trace_multiset_sum

trace_mul_comm:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `matrix.mul -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `matrix.mul -/
theorem trace_mul_comm [add_comm_monoid R] [comm_semigroup R] (A : matrix m n R) (B : matrix n m R) :

trace_list_sum:
@[simp]
theorem trace_list_sum (l : list (matrix n n R)) : trace l.sum = (l.map trace).sum :=
  map_list_sum (trace_add_monoid_hom n R) l
#align trace_list_sum trace_list_sum
trace_fin_zero:
@[simp]
theorem trace_fin_zero (A : matrix (fin 0) (fin 0) R) : trace A = 0 :=
  rfl
#align trace_fin_zero trace_fin_zero
trace_fin_two:
theorem trace_fin_two (A : matrix (fin 2) (fin 2) R) : trace A = A 0 0 + A 1 1 :=
  congr_arg ((· + ·) _) (add_zero (A 1 1))
#align trace_fin_two trace_fin_two
trace_fin_three:
theorem trace_fin_three (A : matrix (fin 3) (fin 3) R) : trace A = A 0 0 + A 1 1 + A 2 2 :=
  by
  rw [← add_zero (A 2 2), add_assoc]
  rfl
#align trace_fin_three trace_fin_three
trace_fin_one:
theorem trace_fin_one (A : matrix (fin 1) (fin 1) R) : trace A = A 0 0 :=
  add_zero _
#align trace_fin_one trace_fin_one
trace_conj_transpose:

@[simp]
theorem trace_conj_transpose [StarAddMonoid R] (A : matrix n n R) : trace (matrix.conj_transpose A) = star (trace A) :=
  (star_sum _ _).symm
#align trace_conj_transpose trace_conj_transpose
trace_col_mul_row:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `matrix.mul -/
@[simp]
theorem trace_col_mul_row [NonUnitalNonAssocSemiring R] (a b : n → R) :
    trace (matrix.mul (col a) (row b)) = dot_product a b := by simp [dot_product, trace]
#align trace_col_mul_row trace_col_mul_row
trace_add:
@[simp]
theorem trace_add (A B : matrix n n R) : trace (A + B) = trace A + trace B :=
  finset.sum_add_distrib
#align trace_add trace_add
